Name: Frisbee For Fun
About the game: Frisbee For FUN! Frisbee is joy, Frisbee is fun! You are a very mischievous kitten that uses helpless chickens as targets. The distance may vary; Chickens will start to run; Portals will appear; The wind will drive you crazy! What to expect? Hit targets, but be careful ... being a bad kitten can have consequences. Freedom to the chickens!
